text: Jelendol is a Slovene place name that may refer to: ;Places *Jelendol, Ribnica, a village in the Municipality of Ribnica, southern Slovenia *Jelendol, Škocjan, a village in the Municipality of Škocjan, southeastern Slovenia *Jelendol, Tržič, a village in the Municipality of Tržič, northwestern Slovenia ;Buildings *Jelendol Partisan Hospital, a hospital built by the Slovene resistance forces in World War II in the forests of the Kočevje Rog
title: Jelendol
